Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico
@roth.azulik @byroth_

node.text:
Zen moments with @hendrickhartono. 🍵 Experience Japanese flair and Balinese spirituality at HOSHINOYA Resorts, a retreat nestled in a jungle that's thriving atop a hill. 🌱

Be in tune with your inner self as you start your day at the Cafe Gazebo overlooking the jungle, and end your day with a swim in the canal-like pools that cut across the resort's premises. 🏊🏼

Sounds divine, right? Let the sounds of the gamelan lead you here to HOSHINOYA Resorts and experience a pleasant mix of Japanese and Balinese hospitality. 🙇🏼

Will you stay here? What is your favorite thing to do while in Bali? 🇮🇩

📸 @hendrickhartono
📍 @hoshinoresorts.official, Bali, Indonesia

node.text:
Be entranced by this paradise located in the charming town of sunny Essaouira! ☀️ If you could be somewhere else right now, would you want to get transported at Jardin Des Douars? 🇲🇦

Ochre structures adorned by striking color palettes will serve as your secret hideaway and starting point in exploring the neighboring ports, beaches, and sand dunes of this charming medina. Buggy excursions on the beach? ATV rides on sand dunes? Surfing, windsurfing, and kitesurfing? Make it happen here at Essaouira's well-kept secret. 🤫

There are so many more we love about Jardin Des Douars, but we'd rather keep it to ourselves because it's better experiencing this stunning hotel! ❤️

Is Morocco on your travel list? Share with us why you want to visit in the comments!
 
📍 @jardindesdouars, Essaouira, Morocco

Experience an elevated tropical lifestyle at @patinamaldives. 🌴 With a choice of sophisticated villas on the beach or over water, all are tastefully furnished with private pools and sustainable amenities. 🌅

Be immersed from the moment you arrive. Relish evening cocktails and canapes at The Portico, enjoy unlimited access to The Fari Beach Club as well as an assortment of other complimentary offerings that make up your flow. Whether you're a marine adventurer going for scuba diving or snorkelling, or the art hunter revelling in the on-island installations, there is always something that captures you. 🌊

💡 BH Tip: Design your own experience! Patina Essentialists will customize your preferences so that you can slow down or be stimulated, all the while experiencing true Maldivian hospitality!

@patinamaldives, Maldives
#patinamaldives

Fall in love with Sicily at the Grand Hotel Timeo with @ananewyork. 💗 The property sits atop Sicilian cliffs with breathtaking views of Mount Etna, a Greek amphitheater, and the terracotta rooftops of Taormina.

Feel like royalty in their gorgeous rooms and luxurious villas, indulge in Sicilian cuisine, and give yourself a moment to rediscover Sicily as experienced by the world's greatest artists, writers, and European aristocracy. 😍

💡 BH Tip: Want to see Mount Etna up close? The hotel offers boat excursions and tours of the volcano! If you're more of a history buff, head to the Teatro Antico Di Taormina by foot just a few steps from the hotel. 🎭

When was your last trip to Sicily? Is Italy on your bucket list? 🇮🇹

📸 @ananewyork
📍 @belmondgrandhoteltimeo, Sicily, Italy

Swimming in mid-air with @hobopeeba. 😎 Connecting both Embassy Gardens and Legacy Building, this world-famous London attraction has captured the world's attention as the first ever Sky Pool with gorgeous, unobstructed views of the city. 🏙

The Embassy Gardens is your access to the Sky Pool, as well as The Orangery and Sky Deck. These rooftop destinations give tenants and their guests a place to unwind, socialize and work in one of the poshest places in London! 

💡BH Tip: While the Sky Pool is truly a marvel you may want to experience, it is highly exclusive for Embassy Gardens tenants and their guests. Best to make friends here and there, yes? 😉

Would you take a dip here? 💦 Share with us your most beautiful memory of London!

node.text:
This is Amanruya: idyllic, chic, and a break from the usual. Imagine strolling in a village-like property, with the scent of pine trees melding with the Aegean sea breeze. ✨

Craving Turkish and Mediterranean meals made from locally sourced ingredients? Decide if you'll be enjoying it poolside, by the beach, in their Anatolian dining pavilion, or in the comfort of your own room! You can never run out of choices here. 😎

If you're the type to go all-in for wellness, Amanruya will definitely give you the most amazing pampering with unforgettable views! Think massages and mani-pedis overlooking the sea. 💅🏼 Ever had pampering with views of the sea? Would you want to experience that in Amanruya? 💆🏼

📍 @amanruya, Bodrum, Turkey
